{"comments":"ARIA Landmark Roles — Page region navigation\n\nLandmarks provide a way to navigate to major sections of a page.\nScreen reader users can jump between landmarks using keyboard shortcuts.\n\n## Best Practices\n- Use exactly one main landmark per page\n- banner and contentinfo should be at the top level\n- Multiple navigation landmarks should have aria-label\n- search is for site-wide search, not page filtering\n\n## HTML5 Mapping\nMany HTML5 elements automatically provide landmarks:\n- <header> (top-level) → banner\n- <nav> → navigation\n- <main> → main\n- <aside> → complementary\n- <footer> (top-level) → contentinfo\n- <form> with accessible name → form\n- <section> with accessible name → region\n\n## Reference\nhttps://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria-1.2/#landmark_roles\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[48,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Accessibility/Landmark.purs","start":[48,3]},"title":"LandmarkBanner"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[49,26],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Accessibility/Landmark.purs","start":[49,3]},"title":"LandmarkComplementary"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[50,24],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Accessibility/Landmark.purs","start":[50,3]},"title":"LandmarkContentinfo"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[51,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Accessibility/Landmark.purs","start":[51,3]},"title":"LandmarkForm"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[52,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Accessibility/Landmark.purs","start":[52,3]},"title":"LandmarkMain"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[53,23],"name":"../../hy